      "title": "On the computational complexity of the Jones and Tutte polynomials",
      "abstract": "We show that determining the Jones polynomial of an alternating link is #P-hard. This is a special case of a wide range of results on the general intractibility of the evaluation of the Tutte polynomial T(M;x,y) of a matroid M except for a few listed special points and curves of the (x,y)-plane"
